<html lang="en">

  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="description" content="CLI diseñado para programadores" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta property="og:url" content="https://lym.shuttleapp.rs/" />
    <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
    <meta property="og:title" content="lym" />
    <meta property="og:description" content="CLI diseñado para programadores" />
    <meta
      property="og:image"
      content="https://opengraph.b-cdn.net/production/documents/6cdf5679-c84f-4c60-aa24-7e6575301de6.png?token=1gGTQGW_uqv6aambswCmA97HJ2azLKo0B2GS2IB6KXo&height=300&width=1200&expires=33245240050"
    />
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
    <meta property="twitter:domain" content="lym.shuttleapp.rs" />
    <meta property="twitter:url" content="https://lym.shuttleapp.rs/" />
    <meta name="twitter:title" content="lym" />
    <meta
      name="twitter:description"
      content="CLI diseñado para programadores"
    />
    <meta
      name="twitter:image"
      content="https://opengraph.b-cdn.net/production/documents/6cdf5679-c84f-4c60-aa24-7e6575301de6.png?token=1gGTQGW_uqv6aambswCmA97HJ2azLKo0B2GS2IB6KXo&height=300&width=1200&expires=33245240050"
    />
    <link
      rel="shortcut icon"
      href="https://res.cloudinary.com/dgs55s8qh/image/upload/v1708711896/ejvon98nvca4d3iallvg.ico"
      type="image/x-icon"
    />
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <title>{{title}}</title>

  </head>

  <body
    class="w-full min-h-screen flex flex-col justify-start px-4 md:px-0 py-10 items-center bg-slate-900 gap-y-10"
  >
    <main class="w-full md:w-[650px] flex justify-between items-center gap-y-3">
      <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl text-gray-200 font-bold">
        <span class="text-violet-400 text-3xl md:text-5xl">{{title}}</span>: CLI
        Toolkit
      </h1>

      <img
        class="w-[55px] h-[40px] md:w-[90px] md:h-[70px]"
        src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dgs55s8qh/image/upload/v1708707058/esu98yo1dlwtfjtiixyk.png"
      />
    </main>
    <p class="text-gray-300 w-full md:w-[650px] text-start text-lg md:text-xl">
      CLI diseñado para programadores
      <span class="text-violet-400">v1.0.0</span>
    </p>

    <div
      class="w-full flex flex-col justify-center items-start md:items-center gap-y-5"
    >
      <p
        class="w-full md:w-[650px] text-gray-200 font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl"
      >
        Instalación
      </p>
      <div
        class="w-full md:w-[650px] flex flex-col justify-start items-start gap-y-2"
      >
        <p class="text-gray-200 text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold">Linux</p>
        <p
          onclick="alert('No está disponible de momento')"
          class="relative w-full md:w-[650px] bg-slate-800 text-white rounded-lg border border-violet-300 py-2 px-3"
        >
          >&nbsp;&nbsp;sudo&nbsp;&nbsp;apt&nbsp;&nbsp;install&nbsp;&nbsp;<span
            class="text-green-400"
          >lym</span>
          <svg
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            class="absolute top-1 right-1 w-8 h-8 duration-75 cursor-pointer hover:scale-110"
          >
            <path
              fill-rule="evenodd"
              clip-rule="evenodd"
              d="M19.5 16.5L19.5 4.5L18.75 3.75H9L8.25 4.5L8.25 7.5L5.25 7.5L4.5 8.25V20.25L5.25 21H15L15.75 20.25V17.25H18.75L19.5 16.5ZM15.75 15.75L15.75 8.25L15 7.5L9.75 7.5V5.25L18 5.25V15.75H15.75ZM6 9L14.25 9L14.25 19.5L6 19.5L6 9Z"
              fill="#c0c0c0"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </p>

      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col justify-start items-start gap-y-2">
        <p class="text-gray-200 text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold">Windows</p>

        <ul
          class="list-decimal relative w-full md:w-[650px] text-white rounded-lg border border-violet-300 py-2 px-8 bg-slate-800 space-y-1.5"
        >
          <li class="text-gray-200 text-md md:text-lg">Descarga la última
            versión de lym
            <a
              href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1dRzWho_11y8oJQICEIlWuHTVlykI87dZ/view?usp=sharing"
              target="_blank"
              class="text-blue-400"
            >aquí</a>.
          </li>
          <li class="text-gray-200 text-md md:text-lg">Para tener acceso global
            a lym tienes 2 opciones:
            <ul class="list-disc pl-3">
              <li class="text-gray-200 text-md md:text-lg"><span
                  class="text-green-300"
                >Recomendado: </span>añadir la ubicación de lym.exe al PATH del
                sistema.
              </li>
              <li class="text-gray-200 text-md md:text-lg"><span
                  class="text-red-400"
                >No recomendado:
                </span>colocar lym.exe dentro del directorio System32.
              </li>

            </ul>
          </li>
          <li class="text-gray-200 text-md md:text-lg">Para actualizar lym
            repite el proceso eliminando la versión anterior.</li>
        </ul>

      </div>

    </div>

    <section class="w-full md:w-[650px] space-y-2 md:space-y-5">
      <h2
        class="text-2xl md:text-3xl text-gray-300 font-bold tracking-tighter"
      >Uso</h2>

      <div
        class="h-max w-full bg-slate-800 rounded-lg border border-violet-300 flex flex-col"
      >
        <div
          class="flex justify-between items-center h-10 px-4 text-gray-200 bg-slate-900 rounded-t-lg"
        >
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="w-6 h-6">

            <path
              d="M4 6H20M4 12H20M4 18H20"
              stroke="#fff"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
            ></path>

          </svg>
          <p>lymcli<span class="text-green-300">@</span>rust</p>
          <div class="flex justify-center items-center">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="yellow" class="w-6 h-6">

              <path
                d="M21 12C21 16.9706 16.9706 21 12 21C7.02944 21 3 16.9706 3 12C3 7.02944 7.02944 3 12 3C16.9706 3 21 7.02944 21 12Z"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
              ></path>

            </svg>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="green" class="w-6 h-6">

              <path
                d="M21 12C21 16.9706 16.9706 21 12 21C7.02944 21 3 16.9706 3 12C3 7.02944 7.02944 3 12 3C16.9706 3 21 7.02944 21 12Z"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
              ></path>

            </svg>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="red" class="w-6 h-6">

              <path
                d="M21 12C21 16.9706 16.9706 21 12 21C7.02944 21 3 16.9706 3 12C3 7.02944 7.02944 3 12 3C16.9706 3 21 7.02944 21 12Z"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
              ></path>

            </svg>

          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="py-4 px-1 md:p-4 flex-1 overflow-auto">
          <div class="grid gap-1.5 text-sm md:text-lg">
            <p class="text-white">
              >&nbsp;&nbsp;lym&nbsp;
              <span class="text-green-400">time</span>
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="grid gap-1.5 text-sm md:text-lg">
            <p class="text-gray-300">
              >&nbsp;12:34:23&nbsp;&nbsp;-&nbsp;&nbsp;23/02/24
            </p>
          </div>
          <br />
          <div class="grid gap-1.5 text-sm md:text-lg">
            <p class="text-white">
              >&nbsp;&nbsp;lym&nbsp;&nbsp;<span
                class="text-green-400"
              >cal&nbsp;</span>
              &apos;(32 * 3)&nbsp;/&nbsp;2&apos;
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="grid gap-1.5 text-sm md:text-lg">
            <p class="text-gray-300">
              >&nbsp;48
            </p>
          </div>
          <br />
          <div class="grid gap-1.5 text-sm md:text-lg">
            <p class="text-white">
              >&nbsp;&nbsp;lym
              <span class="text-green-400">&nbsp;en&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>missing
              initializer in const declaration
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="grid gap-1.5 text-sm md:text-lg">
            <p class="text-gray-300">
              >&nbsp;&nbsp;falta inicializador en la declaración constante
            </p>
          </div>
          <br />
          <div class="grid gap-1.5 text-sm md:text-lg">
            <p class="text-white">
              >&nbsp;&nbsp;lym&nbsp;&nbsp;<span
                class="text-green-400"
              >es&nbsp;</span>
              no hay productos en el carrito
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="grid gap-1.5 text-sm md:text-lg">
            <p class="text-gray-300">
              >&nbsp;&nbsp;no products in the cart
            </p>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section
      class="w-full md:w-[650px] flex flex-col justify-start items-center gap-y-7 md:gap-y-4"
    >
      <div
        class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-start items-start md:items-center gap-y-1 gap-x-3 w-full"
      >
        <code
          class="bg-slate-800 px-1.5 md:px-3 py-0.5 md:py-1 rounded-md text-sm md:text-lg text-white border border-violet-200"
        >lym <span class="text-green-300">time</span></code>
        <p class="text-gray-200 text-sm md:text-lg">
          Devuelve la hora y fecha actual<span class="text-green-300">.</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-start items-start md:items-center md:items-center gap-y-1 gap-x-3 w-full"
      >
        <code
          class="bg-slate-800 px-1.5 md:px-3 py-0.5 md:py-1 rounded-md text-sm md:text-lg text-white border border-violet-200"
        >lym
          <span class="text-green-300">cal</span>
          <span class="text-violet-200">&apos;[</span>expresión<span
            class="text-violet-200"
          >]&apos;</span>
        </code>
        <p class="text-gray-200 text-sm md:text-lg">
          Resuelve expresiones matemáticas<span class="text-green-300">.</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-start items-start md:items-center gap-y-2 gap-x-3 w-full"
      >
        <code
          class="bg-slate-800 px-1.5 md:px-3 py-0.5 md:py-1 rounded-md text-sm md:text-lg text-white border border-violet-200"
        >lym
          <span class="text-green-300">en</span>
          <span class="text-violet-200">[</span>texto<span
            class="text-violet-200"
          >]</span>
        </code>
        <p class="text-gray-200 text-sm md:text-lg">
          Traduce texto de inglés a español<span class="text-green-300">.</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-start items-start md:items-center gap-y-2 gap-x-3 w-full"
      >
        <code
          class="bg-slate-800 px-1.5 md:px-3 py-0.5 md:py-1 rounded-md text-sm md:text-lg text-white border border-violet-200"
        >lym
          <span class="text-green-300">es</span>
          <span class="text-violet-200">[</span>texto<span
            class="text-violet-200"
          >]</span>
        </code>
        <p class="text-gray-200 text-sm md:text-lg">
          Traduce texto de español a inglés<span class="text-green-300">.</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div
        class="flex justify-start items-center w-full text-sm md:text-lg opacity-70"
      >
        <p class="text-white">más comandos proximamente</p>
        <span class="text-green-300">...</span>
      </div>

    </section>

    <footer class="w-full mt-10 text-gray-200 text-center">
      <a
        rel="noreferrer"
        href="https://gixi.me"
        target="_blank"
        className="text-slate-300 text-md sm:text-lg hover:text-white cursor-pointer w-full text-center"
        title="gixi contacto"
      >
        Creado con ❤️ por
        <u>gixi</u>
      </a></footer>
  </body>

</html>